-- Carlyle Group to pay $115 mln in LBO collusion settlement -source
-- By Greg Roumeliotis in New York
-- Fri Aug 29, 2014 07:17PM EDT
-- None



Aug 29 (Reuters) - Carlyle Group LP <CG.O> agreed to pay $115 million to settle a lawsuit that accused it and several other large private equity firms of conspiring not to outbid each other on takeovers prior to the financial crisis, according to a source familiar with the matter.

Carlyle was the only private equity firm among those still facing trial not to have settled